title: Top 10 Wide Receiver Rankings: Julio Jones or Michael Thomas for top spot? (Football 7/2)
description:
With so many great wide receivers in the NFL, Jared Dubin was tasked with creating a list of his Top 10 and discusses that group on today's episode with host Will Brinson. At #10 is a player that has probably been the top guy at some point in his career and could easily be up top again after this season. Which Buc ranks higher: Chris Godwin or Mike Evans? Dubin's a Cowboys fan, so where does he have Amari Cooper? The top 5 are pretty set, it's the order that's up for debate. Find out who cracks the list!
